 <refsect1>
  <title>Compatibility</title>

  <para>
   <command>CREATE AGGREGATE</command> is a
   <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> language extension.  The SQL
   standard does not provide for user-defined aggregate functions.
  </para>
 </refsect1>

